--> Purpose

    The test-cases inside this directory are not covered in the 'Tutorials' section of the user guide of rheoTool. These cases use simple geometries (duct or tube) and are mostly intended to provide a template for all the available constituve equations in rheoTool.
    
    WARNING: never build your own case by simple copy-paste of any tutorial, without checking each relevant parameter!!! 

--> How to run any case inside this directory:

   1. ~$ blockMesh
   2. ~$ rheoFoam
   
   or simply  
   
   ./Allrun
	
	  

